QuestData.Title: Garbage for the Garbage God
QuestData.Description: Richmon, you found a thing I been looking for for a long time. Bring it to me in the Port of Zandalar, and I will grant you my favor.
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: The loa of scavengers is reaching into your mind.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring Jani's First Offering to Jani's Trashpile in the Port of Zandalar.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Bring Jani's First Offering to Jani's Trashpile in the Port of Zandalar.
